# Sukabumi maintenance -- always on
#
# Keeps Pi powered continuously for field maintenance, debugging,
# or software updates. Equivalent to Jakarta's always-on mode.
#
# The OFF S1 is the minimum allowed -- Pi stays on effectively 24/7.
# To exit maintenance: load schedule_15min.wpi or schedule_30min.wpi.

BEGIN 2026-01-01 00:00:00
END   2099-12-31 23:59:59
ON    D1
OFF   S1
